dc_description_s: This data layer represents addresses for Sawyer County, Wisconsin in 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, Sawyer_Addresses_2016.gdb. [The site address is a point feature class that locates sites or address locations. To provide a point for all address locations in the County. This may include multiple addresses at one point.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
